Dear Kenneth Addison: 

This is a reminder that the Job Posting for Public Relations/Marketing Intern is expiring on Tuesday December 10, 2013.

If you wish to extend your posting, you can do so by logging into your CarolinaLink account (http://uncch-csm.symplicity.com/employers) and follow the instructions below:

1- Log into the system with your username (email) & password at:
	 http://uncch-csm.symplicity.com/employers
     (if you do not remember your password, you may email it to yourself 
      from the "Forgot My Password" form on the login page)
2- Click "jobs & internships (non-OCR)" on the top menu bar 
3- Select the job position you wish to EXTEND (click the job title) 
4- Change the 'Expiration Date' to a future date
5- Click SUBMIT!

If your job posting has expired, you can repost the position if you would like to continue to list it:       

1- Log into the system with your username (email) & password at:
	 http://uncch-csm.symplicity.com/employers
     (if you do not remember your password, you may email it to yourself 
      from the "Forgot My Password" form on the login page)
2- Click "jobs & internships (non-OCR)" on the top menu bar 
3- Click on ADD NEW button
4- Select the expired job from the drop down list beside the "Copy Existing" field.
5-Update the job listing and click the SUBMIT button!

If you have any questions, please contact University Career Services.

